# Salesforce Partner Portal 3.0 API
This is the documentation of external APIs used by the partner portal. The interactive documentation can be found here: http://docs.partnerportal1.apiary.io/

To base url for the mocking server is: http://private-4ea14-partnerportal1.apiary-mock.com/

## Group Tokens
Provides client authentication and grant access to API using tokens

## Token [/tokens]

### Get a Token [GET]

+ Request
    + Headers

            grant_type: password
            client_id: ID
            client_secret: SECRET
            username: USER
            password: PASSWORD

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (object, required)
        + token: Qhwej23Jhshw (string, required)

## Group Partners
Provides different data structures for a Partner: partner information, payments, coupons sold.

## Partner [/partners/{partner_id}]

+ Parameters
    + partner_id: 0015700001moHBx (string, required)

### Get a Partner by id [GET]

+ Request
    + Headers

            Authorization: Qhwej23Jhshw

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + name: Muster AG (string, required)
        + website: www.musterag.ch (string, required)
        + address (object, required)
            + street: Musterstrasse 76 (string, required)
            + complement: Postfach 80765 (string)
            + city: Musterstadt (string, required)
            + postal_code: 6754 (string, required)
        + gps_coordinates (object, required)
            + latitude: 47.3775078 (string, required)
            + longitude: 8.5016957 (string, required)

