## Data Structures

### Payment (object)
+ datetime: `2015-05-05T12:30:00` (string, required)
+ collections (array, required)
    + (PaymentCollection)
    + (PaymentCollection)

### PaymentCollection (object)
+ title: Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet (string, required)
+ variants (array, required)
    + (PaymentVariant)
    + (PaymentVariant)

### PaymentVariant (object)
+ price (number, required)

### CouponCollection (object)
+ id: 1 (string, required)
+ online_date: `2015-05-05T12:30:00`(string, required)
+ title: Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet (string, required)
+ deals (array, required)
    + (CouponDeal)
    + (CouponDeal)

### CouponDeal (object)
+ id: 1 (string, required)
+ title: Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet (string, required)
+ coupons (array, required)
    + (Coupon)
    + (Coupon)
        + pin: 1234RT
    + (Coupon)
        + pin: 1234RT

### Coupon (object)
+ number: 1 (number, required)
+ code: 123487TD (string, required)
+ pin (string, required)

